                            <comment id="12830845" author="tcc" created="Mon, 8 Feb 2010 06:13:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch checks for a locale attribute and applies it. If no locale attribute is specified, then the default one on the system is used.&lt;/p&gt;

